            "type": "text",
            "text": "Product Requirements Document \u2014 YouTube Analytics Tool"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Problem Statement"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "YouTube's native analytics are shallow, delayed, and offer no actionable recommendations. Creators making decisions about titles, thumbnails, and posting times are flying blind \u2014 or spending hours cross-referencing third-party tools. The YouTube Analytics Tool is a creator intelligence dashboard that connects directly to the YouTube Data API, surfaces the metrics that actually predict growth, and tells creators exactly what to do next."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Goals"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Surface click-through rate, average view duration, and subscriber conversion by video in real time"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Identify which video topics, formats, and lengths produce the highest subscriber-to-view ratio"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Provide AI-generated recommendations: 'Post this topic on Tuesday at 3pm'"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Compare performance against niche benchmarks to contextualize results"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Core Features"
          }
        ]
